title: New: Clu – Moonrunner (Feat. Gemma Dunlovely)
content: It’s been a minute since we last heard from Irish duo Clu (Sean Cooley and Kevin Freeney), with their gorgeous video for Evening Ever marking them out as a serious talent to keep an ear out for. Part of the blossoming Irish electronic scene sure to cause waves in 2013, their new track Moonrunner, featuring the vocal talents of Gemma Dunlovely, steps up the game yet again. Demanding repeated listens, it’s a track that really embeds itself in the consciousness, with it’s slick R&B vibes and intricate percussion, 2013 better watch out.
author: 5e9b68b27a1236eccfeb1d27
